    "description": {
      "zh": "5.45x39毫米PRS是带有防跳弹弹头的子弹（专门为特种部队和执法部门研发）。",
      "en": "A 5.45x39mm PRS gs cartridge with a 3.9 gram soft lead core bullet with a bimetallic jacket in a steel case. This PRS bullet (Ponízhennoy Rikoshetíruyushchey Sposóbnosti - \"Reduced Ricochet Ability\") was designed in the early 2000s to crumble and rapidly lose speed when hitting a solid object in order to substantially reduce collateral damage from ricochets during urban operations carried out by law enforcement agencies and groups from the Ministry of Internal Affairs, thus achieving a considerable stopping power effect on the target at the cost of penetration capabilities, even against basic ballistic protection."
    },
